dependencyAlias.name: String, actual name of the dependency. e.g.: 'express'
dependencyAlias.execute: boolean, if should or not be executed e.g.: require('express')() <- executed
dependencyAlias.executionPath: String, path to be executed. e.g.: require('http').Server(), 'Server' is the Execution path

executionArguments.alias: String, dependency to be provided as parameter on execution.
